Data input for teal app

dataset.Rd

Abstract function that creates dataset object with connected metadata.

dataset(dataname, data, keys = list(primary = NULL, foreign = NULL,
  parent = NULL), labels = list(dataset_label = NULL, column_labels =
  NULL))

Arguments

dataname

name of dataset
data

data
keys

list of keys
labels

list of labels

Value

a dataset with connected metadata

Examples

library(random.cdisc.data)

ADSL <-  suppressWarnings(radsl(N = 600, seed = 123))

dataset("ADSL", ADSL)
